              "operation": "condition_map",
              "_note": "Phase 3 (separate from ui_template_matrix's UI-layout decision): determines whether the action/type-selection step (legacy 'Step 2') can be skipped because the answer is already unambiguous. Archaeology finding: the legacy builder (prefillSmartQuoteFromOtherTile/sqOpenBuilderPreseeded) already correctly implements this via uncoveredTypes.length === 1 -- this node makes that real, working logic an explicit, auditable rule rather than inline code only discoverable by reading the builder function.",
              "rules": [
                {
                  "if": {
                    "uncovered_service_types_count": 1
                  },
                  "then": {
                    "skip_type_selection": true,
                    "preseed_action_from": "uncovered_service_types[0]"
