              "auto_select_named_service": 70,
              "route_to_group_other_tile": 50,
              "_note": "Archaeology Audit finding: these two confidence thresholds were hardcoded in TWO places each (the legacy sqAnalyze AND the Phase 1 collectBookingContext_freeText collector), never read from the SSOT. auto_select_named_service is the bar a free-text match's _matchConfidence must clear to auto-select a specific named service outright (skip straight to its curated card). route_to_group_other_tile is the lower bar for routing to a resolved GROUP's synthetic Other tile when no single named service is confident enough. Both now live here as the single, real source -- orch_resolve_entity and collectBookingContext_freeText both read from this node instead of each carrying their own duplicate literal."
